00:08:41.921 --> 00:09:17.820 align:middle line:90%


00:09:17.820 --> 00:09:19.110 align:middle line:84%
Since the "Awakening
the Dreamer,

00:09:19.110 --> 00:09:22.060 align:middle line:84%
Changing the Dream" symposium
was launched in 2005,

00:09:22.060 --> 00:09:24.030 align:middle line:84%
it has seen
phenomenal expansions

00:09:24.030 --> 00:09:25.660 align:middle line:90%
throughout the world.

00:09:25.660 --> 00:09:29.030 align:middle line:10%
Thousands and thousands of
trained volunteer facilitators

00:09:29.030 --> 00:09:32.060 align:middle line:10%
are presenting the symposium
in more than 50 countries

00:09:32.060 --> 00:09:34.470 align:middle line:10%
in more than 10 languages.

00:09:34.470 --> 00:09:37.820 align:middle line:84%
Now, thanks to our partnership
with the people at Gaiam,

00:09:37.820 --> 00:09:40.820 align:middle line:84%
we are able to bring this
vital message to millions

00:09:40.820 --> 00:09:44.170 align:middle line:90%
more people worldwide.

00:09:44.170 --> 00:09:47.850 align:middle line:84%
This program aims to recreate
the life-changing experience

00:09:47.850 --> 00:09:51.580 align:middle line:84%
of attending the "Awakening
the Dreamer" symposium.

00:09:51.580 --> 00:09:53.500 align:middle line:84%
You'll be seeing an
actual symposium,

00:09:53.500 --> 00:09:55.810 align:middle line:84%
witnessing the
informative presentations,

00:09:55.810 --> 00:09:58.660 align:middle line:84%
watching powerful
videos, and listening in

00:09:58.660 --> 00:10:01.540 align:middle line:90%
on dynamic group interactions.

00:10:01.540 --> 00:10:05.210 align:middle line:84%
Then, you get to interact
with the material, as well.

00:10:05.210 --> 00:10:07.330 align:middle line:84%
From time to time,
I'll be back to guide

00:10:07.330 --> 00:10:10.270 align:middle line:90%
you through the process.

00:10:10.270 --> 00:10:12.130 align:middle line:84%
The symposium
you're about to see

00:10:12.130 --> 00:10:17.220 align:middle line:84%
was filmed at the Gaiam studios
in Boulder, Colorado, in 2011.

00:10:17.220 --> 00:10:19.460 align:middle line:84%
The participants were
members of the community

00:10:19.460 --> 00:10:21.008 align:middle line:90%
from all walks of life.

00:10:21.008 --> 00:10:23.820 align:middle line:90%


00:10:23.820 --> 00:10:25.340 align:middle line:10%
Well, we'd like to
welcome all of you

00:10:25.340 --> 00:10:28.420 align:middle line:10%
to "Awakening the Dreamer,
Changing the Dream" symposium.

00:10:28.420 --> 00:10:30.260 align:middle line:10%
It's just-- we're--
we're totally

00:10:30.260 --> 00:10:33.760 align:middle line:10%
excited that you're here to
be part of this symposium.

00:10:33.760 --> 00:10:35.410 align:middle line:84%
And we'd like to start
with just having you learn

00:10:35.410 --> 00:10:37.320 align:middle line:90%
a little bit about who we are.

00:10:37.320 --> 00:10:42.310 align:middle line:10%
My name is Doctora Anita
Louisa Theresa Medina Sanchez.

00:10:42.310 --> 00:10:43.920 align:middle line:10%
And you can call me Anita.

