up to my purpose.

00:10:58.430 --> 00:11:00.810 align:middle line:84%
To be a whole human
being means to really

00:11:00.810 --> 00:11:06.270 align:middle line:84%
be conscious of my connection
to people, to the earth,

00:11:06.270 --> 00:11:07.540 align:middle line:90%
and to the sacred.

00:11:07.540 --> 00:11:10.340 align:middle line:84%
And this has allowed
