seeing that this work has

00:11:37.530 --> 00:11:39.530 align:middle line:84%
a way of speaking to
the common interest

00:11:39.530 --> 00:11:41.710 align:middle line:84%
that we have--
that we all share--

00:11:41.710 --> 00:11:44.220 align:middle line:84%
wherever we are from-- for
a whole and healed world.

00:11:44.220 --> 00:11:45.650 align:middle line:90%
I'm just delighted to be here.

00:11:45.650 --> 00:11:47.040 align:middle line:90%
Hi to everybody.

00:11:47.040 --> 00:11:50.500 align:middle line:84%
Welcome, and-- and we're
going to move forward.

00:11:50.500 --> 00:11:52.290 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, let's get on
with the symposium.

00:11:52.290 --> 00:11:53.370 align:middle line:90%
And get going.

